cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.HC

The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically the reconstruction of color images from 3D point clouds obtained through structure from motion. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and rendering, which falls under cs.GR (Computer Graphics). Additionally, the paper deals with machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The privacy attack aspect of the paper could also fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
